name: Too Late 'midnight blue' Original Watch
description:
TOO LATE ORIGINAL WATCH

<iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sillycone.com.au%2Fproduct%2Fmidnight-blue&layout=standard&show_faces=false&width=200&action=like&colorscheme=light&height=35" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:200px; height:35px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>

> Too Late is a unique italian design 
> Too Late watch comes in the jar... not just a prop for fancy photos
> Too Late is available in ten different colors
> Too Late is huge craze in Italy - on the wrist of every Italian in the know

and Too Late gets better ... 

despite being too cool for school, there's heaps of features on the Too Late Orginal Watches that you probably don't know about: 
> waterproof (gym/swimming/beach) 
> 2 years warranty on every Too Late Original Watch
> date and time functions 
> silicon band 

Too Late Original Watches are available in two sizes: 
> medium (18cm perimeter) 
> large (20cm perimeter)

HOW DO I CHOOSE THE RIGHT SIZE? 
As a general rule for the Too Late Original Watches, most women and kids would take a medium (18cm diameter) and most men would take the large size (20cm diameter) but it also depends how firm or loose you would like it around your wrist.

All you need is a tape measure (or equivalent string etc measured at 18/20cm). Wrap it around your wrist and hold it at 18cm and then at 20cm. Which ever is best, order your Too Late watch accordingly.

The Too Late Originial Watches do stretch to get over the largest part of your hand. We don't care how massive your hands are, the watch WILL stretch over so it is imperative you take the right size for your wrist.
